      "parameters": {
        "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\n  body { \n    font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; \n    color: #333; \n    padding: 40px; \n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n  .header { \n    border-bottom: 3px solid #2c3e50; \n    margin-bottom: 20px; \n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n  h1 { color: #2c3e50; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }\n  .fecha { font-size: 14px; color: #7f8c8d; }\n  \n  table { \n    width: 100%; \n    border-collapse: collapse; \n    margin-top: 20px; \n  }\n  th { \n    background-color: #2c3e50; \n    color: white; \n    text-align: left; \n    padding: 12px; \n  }\n  td { padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }\n  \n  /* Efecto de filas intercaladas (Zebra Striping) */\n  tr:nth-child(even) { background-color: #f2f2f2; } /* Gris claro */\n  tr:nth-child(odd) { background-color: #ffffff; }  /* Blanco */\n\n  .totales-container {\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: flex-end;\n  }\n  .totales-tabla { width: 250px; }\n  .totales-tabla td { border: none; padding: 5px 10px; }\n  .total-final { \n    font-weight: bold; \n    font-size: 18px; \n    color: #e67e22; \n    border-top: 2px solid #2c3e50 !important;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1>Cotización de Servicios</h1>\n    <span class=\"fecha\">Fecha: {{ $json.fecha_generacion || new Date().toLocaleDateString() }}</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>Estimado(a) <strong> {{ $json.nombre_cliente }} </strong>,</p>\n  <p>A continuación, presentamos el detalle de los cursos solicitados:</p>\n\n  <table>\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Descripción del Curso</th>\n        <th style=\"text-align: right;\">Precio</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      {{ $json.borrador_ia.split('\\n').filter(line => line.startsWith('- ')).map(curso => {\n         const parts = curso.replace('- ', '').split(': ');\n         return `<tr><td>${parts[0]}</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">${parts[1]}</td></tr>`;\n      }).join('') }}\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <div class=\"totales-container\">\n    <table class=\"totales-tabla\">\n      <tr>\n        <td>Subtotal:</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right;\">$ {{ $('cotizacion total y borrador').item.json.subtotal }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IVA (16%):</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right;\">$ {{ $('cotizacion total y borrador').item.json.iva }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"total-final\">\n        <td>TOTAL:</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right;\">$ {{ $json.total_cotizacion }}</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
      },
